  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育LMS门户设计一个简单的状态流转图。核心场景是：用户在学习过程中，状态会在\"静止\"和\"进行中\"之间切换，极端情况下还可能触发\"崩溃\"状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我理解为：Still代表用户暂停或空闲状态，Moving代表活跃学习状态，Crash是系统异常。请问这三个状态之间都是双向流转吗？特别是Crash之后能直接恢复吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "不是完全双向。Still和Moving之间可以互相切换，这没问题。但Crash比较特殊——崩溃后系统要重置，所以只能从Crash回到门户入口，不能直接回到Still或Moving。另外，门户入口本身也要能进入Still状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，我梳理一下：Education_LMS_Portal作为入口，可以进入Still；Still和Moving双向互通；Moving可以进入Crash；Crash只能返回Education_LMS_Portal。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。不过还有个小细节——Still状态其实也能直接返回门户入口，比如用户主动退出学习回到首页。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "收到，我这就画出来。标题定为\"Simple sample\"，用stateDiagram-v2语法。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Simple sample",
        "stateDiagram-v2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "画好了。结构是：门户入口与Still双向连接，Still与Moving双向连接，Moving单向指向Crash，Crash单向返回门户入口。您看看是否符合预期？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题，这个流转逻辑准确反映了我们的教育LMS状态设计。可以定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
